{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"fb9bdbdd7bcd512a18215dc008698c6ad228f98447bf245879d7be086cef8301","slug":"org","location":"/handbook/qtclass/org.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"量潮课堂组织架构","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/handbook/qtclass/org.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/handbook/qtclass/org.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"org.md","url":"/org-827a8f89496ba0330a159f178b79ea2f.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本文为团队和学生梳理当前量潮课堂复杂的组织架构，以方便接下来组织课程与实训。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"KmuAfhAqt0"}],"key":"kcZJOnBoPU"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"量潮课堂现行的课程体系主要包括理论课和实践课两个系统，服务模型分别是课程和实训。","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"x7FlGkMDln"}],"key":"zNvU6gHeZl"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"理论课的基本单位是微专业和班级。目前我们主要在运营“量潮大数据微专业”及浙理班级、社会招生班级。浙理班级即为我们负责运营的浙江理工大学大数据微专业的教学班级。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"HASI7HM61h"}],"key":"e0nTtXZUf1"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"实训课的基本单位是实训基地和训练营。目前我们主要在运营“量潮实训基地”和“大数据训练营”、“CEO助理训练营”、以及以 VIP 学员为单位的数个“VIP训练营”。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"wlqWNpBWch"}],"key":"O90sNekpHZ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"学生可以根据自己的学习意向报名不同的班级和训练营。付费学员免审核购买课程和实训，VIP 学员免审核任何我们开设的课程的特权。免费学员需要遵循我们的选拔框架参与各项入选和阶段性考核，我们会淘汰无法回馈课堂的学员。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"F5elEMzamG"}],"key":"iHvt1pzCP6"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"量潮科技委托量潮课堂事业部负责运营量潮课堂、秘书处复核。运营团队的主要职责是管理各班级和训练营、与学员协商制定和发布各项工作章程等。事业部对公司的营收、人才供给、交付供给等负责。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"WsSnuMi5OT"}],"key":"OpTmqywemz"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"量潮课堂主要通过社会招生和校企合作两种方式招生。社会招生主要参考和延伸现行的人力资源管理办法到微专业和实训基地。校企合作在社会招生的基础上，根据校企合作协议免审核。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"ZBtNSbUkBb"}],"key":"U3L3v8vGMi"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希望参与各方可以遵守共同执行的工作契约。我们也感谢各方让渡教育领导权，并会珍惜这份来之不易的信任。如果有参与方违背我们的共同契约，我们会毫不犹豫地采取坚决措施处理。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"L2erd6rXnC"}],"key":"HeX9LmtJWL"}],"key":"BvLOmvN4sw"}],"key":"m0rLe8Uats"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}